creator: APPS INNOVA
descriptionHtml:
Local Weather provides you with intimate weather service no matter what city you are in with accurate weather forecasts to take care of your trip.

== Special Features ==
[ 24x7 local & national real-time weather info]
Displays current weather conditions for exact position you are. Include both domestic and international weather information which is adopted from multiple meteorological authority.
Offers weather forecast for any place up to 15 days in advance to help you planing a trip.
Weather conditions are updated every minutes in Local Weather so that you can check the latest and accurate weather forecast at any time.

[Severe Weather alert]
Local Weather provides instant notifications of over 300 types of potential severe weather sourced from government weather agencies according to your position and displays accordingly disaster countermeasures to you in order to protect your life.
Potential severe weather includes persistent high temperatures, hurricanes, tornadoes, thunderstorms, blizzards, storms, floods, tsunamis, forest fires, radiation hazards, agriculture, and livestock etc. for full range of weather services.

[Accurate Hourly Weather Forecast]
Detailed 24 hours weather forecast, including temperatures, air quality index (AQI), UV index, humidity, visibility, wind direction, wind speed, pressure changes etc. can be seen in weather forecast.
Provides user-friendly visualized data elements such as rainfall area, severe weather area, temperature trends and so on.

[Radar maps to track hazardous weather conditions]
Provides highly responsive interactive radar maps so that you can switch between radar, high-resolution satellite and rainfall maps to obtain real-time snowfall and rainfall tracking data with different purposes.
Powerful, easy-to-use radar helps tracking lightning, hurricanes, and tornadoes to protect you and your assets from severe weather.
